<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Newsletter Subscription</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
                <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">Thank you for subscribing!</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hello,</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; background-color: #ecf0f1; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #3498db;">
                    We have successfully received your subscription to our newsletter.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;">You’ll now receive the latest updates, offers, and articles directly in your inbox.</p>
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                    <a href="<%= unsubscribeLink %>" style="background-color: #3498db; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; transition: background-color 0.3s ease;">Unsubscribe</a>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #7f8c8d; text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;">
        © 2024 Your Platform. All rights reserved.
    </p>
</body>
</html>